1 -> create  virtual env           [ python3 -m venv  [envname] ] 
2 -> activate the virtual env      [ source  envname/bin/activate ]
3 -> install the required modules  [ python3  -m pip  install -r requirement.txt ]
4 -> build  internal lib           [ python3  setup.py  build ]  
5 -> build  internal lib           [ python3  setup.py  install ]  
6 -> have fun  !!                 

* python3  ocv_gs.py -h    ( for help )   
